beta1 methods

beta1 returns a vector with all the estimated values of the \(d_i = \beta_1 u_i + \beta_2 w_i + \epsilon_i\) models fitted by ChIPexoQual

beta1(object)

# S4 method for ExoData
beta1(object)

Arguments

object
a ExoData object.

Value

A numeric vector with estimated values for \(\beta_1\).

Examples

data(exoExample)
